{"tid":83124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁大嘥? 過萬包能得利丟在垃圾站","createTime":"2017-01-16T13:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T02:51:31.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"541822ffb5b4a44c9b5f7dab851f8879c96cf1bb","tid":83124,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:22:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2017-01-15_22-46-55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F2017-01-15_22-46-55.jpg&h=18c5592f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n017/01/16 (週一) 12:00上午<br />\n<br />\n點解咁大嘥? 過萬包能得利丟在垃圾站<br />\n食物珍貴，但仍有不少人做「大嘥鬼」！facebook有專頁發帖指，昨午在元朗大樹下東路塘頭埔村附近，有三大板、估計有過萬筒過了「此日期前最佳」的橡皮糖被棄置，有部分更是標明今年1月未過期。不少市民不忍浪費立即前去救糖！有環保團體認為食品商貨倉管理有問題；同時希望大眾理解「此日期前最佳」及「此日期前食用」有分別，即使過了「此日期前最佳」並非等於不能食用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2017-01-15_22-46-55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F2017-01-15_22-46-55.jpg&h=18c5592f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%92%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%98%A5-%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC%E5%8C%85%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%97%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%AB%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metrodaily.hk%2Fmetro_news%2F%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2598%25A5-%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25B8%259F%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25AB%2599%2F&d=%2FwY0s8x9hsXdpF5SfaepXAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2ef8f5ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metrodaily.hk/metro_news/%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%92%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%98%A5-%E9%81%8E%E8%90%AC%E5%8C%85%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%97%E5%88%A9%E4%B8%9F%E5%9C%A8%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%AB%99/</a><br />\n<br />\n點解唔學下連登